    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>extending on @hovanessyan answer.</p>\n\n<p>A basic profile for enabling the downloadSources and downloadJavadocs, in Maven's settings.xml will look like this. \ne.g. profile id is downloadSources</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;!-- add the profile under profiles section --&gt;\n\n    &lt;profile&gt;\n        &lt;id&gt;downloadSources&lt;/id&gt;\n        &lt;properties&gt;\n            &lt;downloadSources&gt;true&lt;/downloadSources&gt;\n            &lt;downloadJavadocs&gt;true&lt;/downloadJavadocs&gt;           \n        &lt;/properties&gt;\n    &lt;/profile&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- activate the profile under activeProfiles section --&gt;\n\n  &lt;activeProfiles&gt;\n    &lt;activeProfile&gt;downloadSources&lt;/activeProfile&gt;\n  &lt;/activeProfiles&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
